1. Onima* koji su strpljivi, sve će doći na svoje vreme. (For those who are patient, everything will come in its time.)
2. Onima* koji su se trudili, nagrađeno je njihovo napredovanje. (Those who have worked hard have been rewarded for their progress.)
3. Onima* koji nisu znali kako da reaguju, dana je prilika za učenje. (Those who did not know how to react were given the opportunity to learn.)
4. Onima* koji su bili tu da pomognu, neizmerno je zahvalnost iskazana. (Those who were there to help were shown immense gratitude.)
5. Onima* koji su bili u nevolji, ponuđena je pomoć. (Those who were in distress were offered help.)